# /middleware — Express middleware functions (request pipeline interceptors)
# Middleware runs before controllers to handle cross-cutting concerns.
# Examples:
#   authMiddleware.js     → JWT verification & req.user population
#   errorHandler.js       → Global error-catching middleware (last in chain)
#   rateLimiter.js        → Request rate limiting per IP / user
#   requestLogger.js      → HTTP request/response logging
#   validate.js           → Schema validation runner (ties into /validators)
#   cors.js               → Custom CORS configuration middleware
#   upload.js             → Multer file-upload handling
